{
    "kp5:0.1_0": "The short topics",
    "kp5:0.2_0": "headed feet",
    "kp5:1.1_0": "So I have heard.",
    "kp5:1.2_0": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery.",
    "kp5:1.3_0": "Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, and,",
    "kp5:1.3_1": "bowed down to the Buddha,",
    "kp5:1.4_0": "That deity addressed the Buddha in verse:",
    "kp5:10.1_0": "Patience, being easy to admonish,",
    "kp5:10.2_0": "the sight of ascetics,",
    "kp5:10.3_0": "and talk on the right time,",
    "kp5:10.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:11.1_0": "Roring austerity and spiritual practice,",
    "kp5:11.2_0": "seeing the noble truths,",
    "kp5:11.3_0": "and realization of extinguishment:",
    "kp5:11.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:12.1_0": "Though touched by worldly conditions,",
    "kp5:12.2_0": "their mind does not tremble;",
    "kp5:12.3_0": "sorrowless, stainless, secure:",
    "kp5:12.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:13.1_0": "Having completed these things,",
    "kp5:13.2_0": "undefeated everywhere;",
    "kp5:13.3_0": "everywhere they go in safety:",
    "kp5:13.4_0": "this is their highest blessing.”",
    "kp5:14.1_0": "With its roots and tubers.",
    "kp5:2.1_0": "“These gods and humans,",
    "kp5:2.2_0": "have thought about blessings",
    "kp5:2.3_0": "desiring well-being:",
    "kp5:2.4_0": "declare the highest blessing.”",
    "kp5:3.1_0": "“Not associating with fools,",
    "kp5:3.2_0": "associating with the wise,",
    "kp5:3.3_0": "and honoring those worthy of honor:",
    "kp5:3.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:4.1_0": "Living in a suitable region,",
    "kp5:4.2_0": "having made merit in the past,",
    "kp5:4.3_0": "being rightly resolved in oneself,",
    "kp5:4.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:5.1_0": "Education and a craft,",
    "kp5:5.2_0": "discipline and training,",
    "kp5:5.3_0": "eloquent speech is fruitful",
    "kp5:5.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:6.1_0": "Caring for mother and father,",
    "kp5:6.2_0": "kindness to children and partners,",
    "kp5:6.3_0": "and unstressful work:",
    "kp5:6.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:7.1_0": "Giving and righteous conduct,",
    "kp5:7.2_0": "kindness to relatives,",
    "kp5:7.3_0": "blameless deeds:",
    "kp5:7.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:8.1_0": "Desisting and abstaining from evil,",
    "kp5:8.2_0": "avoiding alcoholic drinks,",
    "kp5:8.3_0": "diligence in good qualities:",
    "kp5:8.4_0": "this is the highest blessing.",
    "kp5:9.1_0": "Respect and humility,",
    "kp5:9.2_0": "contentment and gratitude,",
    "kp5:9.3_0": "and timely listening to the teaching:",
    "kp5:9.4_0": "this is the highest blessing."
}